Class TerminalValidateResponseDTO

java.lang.Object
common.dto.TerminalValidateResponseDTO
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class TerminalValidateResponseDTO extends Object implements Serializable
Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing the response for validating a reservation or waiting list code at the terminal.

Used both for validation and for check-in responses.
